other_tests.findings: A novel homozygous missense mutation S129P in FGF23 was identified.
32-kDa protein species (O-glycosylated FGF23) was undetectable in cells expressing [P129]hFGF23, indicating poor secretion compared to wild-type FGF23.
other_tests.changes_over_time: Similar results were obtained for cells expressing [G71]hFGF23 and [F129]hFGF23.
